          O notes: A short year after releasing their highly successful previous       O
          8        album, Universal, Mantrix are back.                                 8
          8                                                                            8
          8        Following up with an album that will knock their fans for a six.    8
          8        Neoteric, Mantrix&#039;s latest album explores the next level of their   8
          8        ever evolving influences in trance music. This time they deliver a  8
          8        more modern Electro Trance vibe suited to a wide range of today&#039;s   8
          8        diverse dancefloors.                                                8
          8                                                                            8
          8        With their usual high level of studio production and compositional  8
          8        brilliance, Mantrix have not only created something to keep their   8
          8        large fan base extremely happy, but also to reach further into many 8
          8        areas of electronica than ever before. This pumping album blends    8
          8        Psy-Trance with Progressive, Tribal, Glitch, Breaks and everything  8
          8        in between.                                                         8
          8                                                                            8
          8        Neoteric is a must for anyone who likes their music fresh,          8
          8        interesting and exciting.                                           8
